Class SimCore.id

  • java.lang.Object
    • plptool.mips.SimCore.id
  • Enclosing class:
    SimCore

    public class SimCore.id
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the instruction decode (ID) / register file (RF) stage of the PLP CPU core. The execute module and the register file are attached to this class.
